      "content": "i'm a bit nervous about calling the surgeon again, they seem so busy and i don't want to be a bother if it's nothing. do you think i can just treat it myself for a day or two? i have some antibiotic cream in my medicine cabinet and i could just do a warm compress on it to help the drainage. would that be okay to try first?",
